INSERT INTO `song` VALUES (75, 11, 'Eminem-When I\'m Gone', 'When I\'m Gone', '2019-06-02 16:42:25', '2022-04-14 15:53:00', '/img/songPic/6656443395492431.jpg', '[00:01.080]Yeah...\n[00:03.499]It\'s my life...\n[00:04.200]My own words I guess...\n[00:06.400]\n[00:06.810]Have you ever loved someone so much, you\'d give an arm for?\n[00:10.060]Not the expression, no, literally give an arm for?\n[00:13.160]When they know they\'re your heart\n[00:14.800]And you know you were their armor and you will destroy anyone who would try to harm her\n[00:19.800]But what happens when karma, turns right around and bites you?\n[00:23.020]And everything you stand for, turns on you, to spite you?\n[00:26.030]What happens when you become the main source of a pain?\n[00:28.910]\"Daddy look what I made\", Dad\'s gotta go catch a plane\n[00:32.220]\"Daddy where\'s Mommy? I can\'t find Mommy where is she?\"\n[00:35.999]I don\'t know go play Hailie, baby, your Daddy\'s busy\n[00:39.100]Daddy\'s writing this song, this song ain\'t gonna write itself\n[00:41.880]I\'ll give you one underdog then you gotta swing by yourself\n[00:44.910]Then turn right around on that song and tell her you love her\n[00:48.800]And put hands on her mother, who\'s a spitting image of her\n[00:51.700]That\'s Slim Shady, yeah baby, Slim Shady\'s crazy\n[00:54.910]Shady made me, but tonight Shady\'s rocka-by-baby...\n[00:58.130]\n[00:58.770]And when I\'m gone, just carry on, don\'t mourn\n[01:01.100]Rejoice every time you hear the sound of my voice\n[01:04.800]Just know that I\'m looking down on you smiling\n[01:06.850]And I didn\'t feel a thing, So baby don\'t feel no pain\n[01:11.000]Just smile back\n[01:11.990]And when I\'m gone, just carry on, don\'t mourn\n[01:14.300]Rejoice every time you hear the sound of my voice\n[01:17.800]Just know that I\'m looking down on you smiling\n[01:20.240]And I didn\'t feel a thing, So baby don\'t feel no pain\n[01:23.210]Just smile back...\n[01:24.620]\n[01:25.450]I keep having this dream, I\'m pushin\' Hailie on the swing\n[01:28.500]She keeps screaming, she don\'t want me to sing\n[01:31.199]\"You\'re making Mommy cry, why? Why is Mommy crying?\"\n[01:34.650]Baby, Daddy ain\'t leaving no more, \"Daddy you\'re lying\n[01:38.390]\"You always say that, you always say this is the last time\n[01:40.979]\"But you ain\'t leaving no more, Daddy you\'re mine\"\n[01:44.100]She\'s piling boxes in front of the door trying to block it\n[01:47.279]\"Daddy please, Daddy don\'t leave, Daddy - no stop it!\"\n[01:50.369]Goes in her pocket, pulls out a tiny necklace locket\n[01:54.200]It\'s got a picture, \"this\'ll keep you safe Daddy, take it withcha\'\"\n[01:57.330]I look up, it\'s just me standing in the mirror\n[02:00.039]These ******\' walls must be talking, cuz man I can hear \'em\n[02:03.340]They\'re saying \"You\'ve got one more chance to do right\" - and it\'s tonight\n[02:06.950]Now go out there and show that you love \'em before it\'s too late\n[02:10.169]And just as I go to walk out of my bedroom door\n[02:12.910]It\'s turns to a stage, they\'re gone, and this spotlight is on\n[02:16.260]And I\'m singing...\n[02:17.050]\n[02:17.270]And when I\'m gone, just carry on, don\'t mourn\n[02:19.320]Rejoice every time you hear the sound of my voice\n[02:22.320]Just know that I\'m looking down on you smiling\n[02:24.950]And I didn\'t feel a thing, So baby don\'t feel no pain\n[02:28.270]Just smile back\n[02:29.800]And when I\'m gone, just carry on, don\'t mourn\n[02:32.290]Rejoice every time you hear the sound of my voice\n[02:35.180]Just know that I\'m looking down on you smiling\n[02:37.730]And I didn\'t feel a thing, So baby don\'t feel no pain\n[02:41.100]Just smile back...\n[02:41.910]\n[02:42.150]Sixty thousand people, all jumping out their seat\n[02:44.629]The curtain closes, they\'re throwing roses at my feet\n[02:47.740]I take a bow and thank you all for coming out\n[02:50.800]They\'re screaming so loud, I take one last look at the crowd\n[02:54.410]I glance down, I don\'t believe what I\'m seeing\n[02:57.480]\"Daddy it\'s me, help Mommy, her wrists are bleeding,\"\n[03:00.920]But baby we\'re in Sweden, how did you get to Sweden?\n[03:04.020]\"I followed you Daddy, you told me that you weren\'t leavin\'\n[03:07.390]\"You lied to me Dad, and now you make Mommy sad\n[03:10.010]\"And I bought you this coin, it says \'Number One Dad\'\n[03:13.470]\"That\'s all I wanted, I just want to give you this coin\n[03:16.630]\"I get the point - fine, me and Mommy are gone\"\n[03:19.920]But baby wait, \"it\'s too late Dad, you made the choice\n[03:22.940]\"Now go up there and show \'em that you love \'em more than us\"\n[03:26.470]That\'s what they want, they want you Marshall, they keep.. screamin\' your name\n[03:30.129]It\'s no wonder you can\'t go to sleep, just take another pill\n[03:35.350]Yeah, I bet you you will. You rap about it, yeah, word, k-keep it real\n[03:39.120]I hear applause, all this time I couldn\'t see\n[03:42.320]How could it be, that the curtain is closing on me\n[03:45.250]I turn around, find a gun on the ground, cock it\n[03:48.770]Put it to my brain and scream \"die Shady\" and pop it\n[03:51.980]The sky darkens, my life flashes, the plane that I was supposed to be on crashes and burns to ashes\n[03:57.340]That\'s when I wake up, alarm clock\'s ringin\', there\'s birds singin\'\n[04:02.350]It\'s Spring and Hailie\'s outside swinging, I walk up to Kim and kiss her\n[04:07.300]Tell her I miss her, Hailie just smiles and winks at her little sister\n[04:11.110]Almost as if to say..\n[04:12.170]\n[04:12.400]And when I\'m gone, just carry on, don\'t mourn\n[04:15.300]Rejoice every time you hear the sound of my voice\n[04:17.660]Just know that I\'m looking down on you smiling\n[04:19.910]And I didn\'t feel a thing, So baby don\'t feel no pain\n[04:23.620]Just smile back\n[04:24.690]And when I\'m gone, just carry on, don\'t mourn\n[04:27.410]Rejoice every time you hear the sound of my voice\n[04:30.290]Just know that I\'m looking down on you smiling\n[04:33.100]And I didn\'t feel a thing, So baby don\'t feel no pain\n[04:36.450]Just smile back...\n[04:38.350]', '/song/Eminem-When I\'m Gone.mp3', NULL);
