I\'m kneading dough\r\n[02:34.75]Pizza boy, I\'m speeding for ya\r\n[02:37.49]We can get married tonight if you really wanna\r\n[02:40.64]Me in a cheap suit like a sleazy lawyer\r\n[02:43.52]And if you break this little heart, it had be an honour\r\n[02:46.91]You don\'t have to say I love you to say I love you\r\n[02:52.49]Forget all the shooting stars and all the silver moons\r\n[02:58.52]We\'ve been making shades of purple out of red and blue\r\n[03:04.42]Sickeningly sweet like honey, don\'t need money\r\n[03:08.20]All I need is you\r\n[03:14.05]All I need is you', '/song/1649932861315.mp3', NULL);
